Collections.rule:
Individual: @B*
Types: Quote
Annotations: rdfs:label @B*
Facts: quote_text @B*,
isQuoteOf @A*

Individual: @C*
Types: Review
Annotations: rdfs:label @C*
Facts: date @C*,
rating @D*,
text @E*,
isReviewOf @A*,
writtenBy @B*

Individual: @A*
	Types: Book
	Annotations: rdfs:label @A* 
	Facts: id @A*,
		title @B*, 
		description @C*, 
		isbn @D*, 
		publish_date @E*, 
		average_rating @F*,
		pages @G*,
		num_reviews @H*,
		num_ratings @I*,
		language_code @J*,
		image_url @K*,
		reviews_widget @L*

Individual: @B*
Types: Genre
Annotations: rdfs:label @B*
Facts: genre_name @B*,
isGenreOf @A*

Individual: @B*
	Types: Work
	Annotations: rdfs:label @B* 
	Facts: original_title @B*, 
		original_publication_date @C*, 
		books_count @D*, 
		reviews_count @E*, 
		ratings_count @F*,
		ratings_sum @G*,
		text_reviews_count @H*,
		rating_dist @I*,
		isWorkOf @A*

Individual: @B*
Types: Reviewer
Annotations: rdfs:label @B*
Facts: name @B*,
wrote @C*

Individual: @B*
Types: Author
Annotations: rdfs:label @B*
Facts: author_id @B*,
name @C*,
author_ratings_count @D*,
born_at @E*,
died_at @F*,
gender @G*,
hometown @H*,
reviews_count @I*,
works_count @J*,
isAuthorOf @A*
